title: Yavapai County Voting Precincts
name: Yavapai County Voting Precincts
description: Election Precincts specify geographic areas that have the same polling location. All people residing within each individual precinct will poll at the same given location. These precincts are the basis from which Supervisor, Legislative, Judicial, Congressional and College Districts are derived.
